Astarta Holding NV (AST) , a Ukrainian
agricultural company and sugar producer, signed a five-year $25
million loan agreement with Citibank, the company said.  Astarta will use the loan to upgrade production capacities
and for acquisition of modern equipment, the Kiev-based company
said in e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
